	* Makefile (sc_cpp_indent_check): Exempt stdio-read.c and stdio-write.c
	per Bruno's request, to accommodate this idiom (no space after "#")
	even when the function is inside an #if block:
	char *
	gets (char *s)
	#undef gets
	{
	  ...
	}

