	* lib/mbsnrtowcs-impl.h: New file, extracted from lib/mbsnrtowcs.c.
	* lib/mbsnrtowcs.c: Include it.
	* modules/mbsnrtowcs (Files): Add lib/mbsnrtowcs-impl.h.

