	* m4/dup2.m4 (gl_FUNC_DUP2): Test for bug.
	* lib/dup2.c (rpl_dup2) [!WIN32]: Add workaround.
	* doc/posix-functions/dup2.texi (dup2): Document the bug.
	* tests/test-dup2.c (main): Enhance test.

