	* lib/arpa_inet.in.h (inet_ntop): Use _GL_CXXALIAS_SYS_CAST instead of
	_GL_CXXALIAS_SYS.
	Reported by Joachim Schmitz <jojo@schmitz-digital.de>.

2010-12-26  Bruno Haible  <bruno@clisp.org>

