	New module 'poll-h'.
	* lib/poll.in.h: Include c++defs.h and warn-on-use.h.
	(poll): Use modern idiom.
	* modules/poll-h: New file.
	* modules/poll (Files): Remove lib/poll.in.h.
	(Depends-on): Add poll-h.
