	FreeBSD.
	* m4/strcasestr.m4 (gl_FUNC_STRCASESTR): Likewise.
	* m4/memmem.m4 (gl_FUNC_MEMMEM): Likewise.

	tests: silence clang warning
	* tests/test-malloca.c (do_allocation): Avoid dead store.

