	* doc/glibc-functions/xdr_short.texi (xdr_short): Likewise.
	* doc/glibc-functions/xdr_sizeof.texi (xdr_sizeof): Likewise.
	* doc/glibc-functions/xdr_string.texi (xdr_string): Likewise.
