	vasnprintf test: Reduce code duplication.
	* tests/test-vasnprintf.c (test_function): New function, extracted from
	test_vasnprintf.
	(test_vasnprintf, test_asnprintf): Invoke it.

2010-04-10  Bruno Haible  <bruno@clisp.org>

