	gnulib-tool: Add support for --libtool in --create-testdir.
	* gnulib-tool (LIBTOOLPATH, LIBTOOLIZE): New variables.
	(func_create_testdir): Emit LT_INIT invocations. Invoke LIBTOOLIZE.

