	xstrtoll: new module
	* modules/xstrtoll: New file.
	* MODULES.html.sh (Numeric conversion functions): Add xstrtoll.
	* lib/xstrtol.h [HAVE_LONG_LONG_INT]: Declare xstrtoll and xstrtoull.
