	Implement nproc for IRIX.
	* lib/nproc.c: Include <sys/sysmp.h>.
	(num_processors): On IRIX systems, try sysmp.
	* m4/nproc.m4 (gl_PREREQ_NPROC): Check for sys/sysmp.h and sysmp.

