	    Bruno Haible  <bruno@clisp.org>

	Implement nproc for NetBSD, OpenBSD.
	* lib/nproc.c: Include <sys/types.h>, <sys/param.h>, <sys/sysctl.h>.
	(ARRAY_SIZE): New macro.
	(num_processors): On BSD systems, try sysctl of HW_NCPU.
