	(gl_FUNC_LINK_FOLLOWS_SYMLINK): ...to this.  Change
	cross-compilation results to -1, to make linkat easier to
	implement when cross-compiling.  Trivially support mingw.
	* modules/link-follow (configure.ac): Call new name.
	* NEWS: Mention this.

