	HAVE_ISNAN[FDL].
	* tests/test-isnanf.c: Include <math.h> instead of isnanf.h.
	* tests/test-isnand.c: Include <math.h> instead of isnand.h.
	* tests/test-isnanl.c: Include <math.h> instead of isnanl.h.
	* NEWS: Mention the change.

