2008-08-17  Bruno Haible  <bruno@clisp.org>

	New module 'threadlib'.
	* modules/threadlib: New file.
	* lib/glthread/threadlib.c: New file, extracted from
	lib/glthread/lock.c.
	* lib/glthread/lock.c (dummy_thread_func, glthread_in_use): Remove
	functions.
