	Tweak "gnulib --version" output.
	* gnulib-tool (func_version): Replace "-dirty" suffix with "-modified".

2008-03-23  Bruno Haible  <bruno@clisp.org>

	Tweak "gnulib --version" output.
	* gnulib-tool (func_version): Use date of last commit to ChangeLog,
