	* m4/vfprintf-posix.m4 (gl_FUNC_VFPRINTF_POSIX): Likewise.
	* m4/vsnprintf-posix.m4 (gl_FUNC_VSNPRINTF_POSIX): Likewise.
	* m4/vsprintf-posix.m4 (gl_FUNC_VSPRINTF_POSIX): Likewise.
