	HAVE_DECL_CEILF, REPLACE_CEILL instead of HAVE_DECL_CEILL,
	REPLACE_FLOORF instead of HAVE_DECL_FLOORF, REPLACE_FLOORL instead of
	HAVE_DECL_FLOORL.

