	* m4/strndup.m4 (gl_FUNC_STRNDUP): Likewise.
	* m4/strnlen.m4 (gl_FUNC_STRNLEN): Likewise.
	* m4/strsep.m4 (gl_FUNC_STRSEP): Likewise.
