2007-08-07  Bruno Haible  <bruno@clisp.org>

	* m4/inttypes.m4 (gl_INTTYPES_H): Use GL_TRIGGER_STDC_LIMIT_MACROS
	instead of __STDC_LIMIT_MACROS_TRIGGER. This avoids a redefinition
	warning from gcc.
	Reported by Eric Blake.

