	gl_SIGNAL_H_DEFAULTS. Set HAVE_POSIX_SIGNALBLOCKING as a shell variable.
	(gl_PREREQ_SIGPROCMASK): Require gl_SIGNAL_H_DEFAULTS. Set
	HAVE_SIGSET_T as a shell variable.
