	* lib/printf-parse.c [!IN_LIBINTL]: Include <stdint.h>, for intmax_t.
	(PRINTF_PARSE): Make the support for size specifier 'j' unconditional.
	* modules/vasnprintf (Depends-on): Add stdint.

