2007-02-26  Ben Pfaff  <blp@cs.stanford.edu>
	    Bruno Haible  <bruno@clisp.org>

	* build-aux/install-reloc: Compile also c-ctype.c.
	* build-aux/relocatable.sh.in: New file.
