	(configure.ac): Invoke gl_STDIO_MODULE_INDICATOR.
	(Include): Use <stdio.h> instead of snprintf.h.
	* m4/snprintf.m4 (gl_FUNC_SNPRINTF): Require gl_STDIO_H_DEFAULTS. Set
