	* lib/striconveh.c (mem_cd_iconveh_internal): Ignore *lengthp if
	*resultp is 0.

	* lib/unistr/u16-to-u8.c (u16_to_u8): Fix u8_uctomb invocation.
	* lib/unistr/u32-to-u8.c (u32_to_u8): Likewise.
