	* modules/gettimeofday (Files): Add lib/gettimeofday.h.
	(configure.ac): Remove AC_FUNC_GETTIMEOFDAY_CLOBBER. Add
	gl_FUNC_GETTIMEOFDAY.
	(Include): Add gettimeofday.h.
