	(Depends-on): Add unitypes.
	* lib/utf16-ucs4.h: Add double-inclusion guard. Include unitypes.h.
	(u16_mbtouc_aux): Move out to separate file.
	(u16_mbtouc): Use ucs4_t, uint16_t types.
	* lib/unistr/utf16-ucs4.c: New file.

