	* modules/alloca-opt (alloca.h): Add a "DO NOT EDIT" comment.
	* modules/argz (argz.h): Likewise.
	* modules/arpa_inet (arpa/inet.h): Likewise.
	* modules/byteswap (byteswap.h): Likewise.
