	Sync from coreutils.

	* lib/getloadavg.c (getloadavg) [__CYGWIN__]: Port to cygwin.
	[__linux__]: Allocate a big enough buffer for /proc/loadavg.
	[!LDAV_DONE]: Avoid unused variable warning.

