2005-09-16  Paul Eggert  <eggert@cs.ucla.edu>

	* lib/stat-time.h: New file.
	* lib/timespec.h (ST_TIME_CMP_NS, ST_TIME_CMP, ATIME_CMP, CTIME_CMP):
