	Document merge from coreutils.
	* modules/alloca: Append $(ALLOCA_H) to BUILT_SOURCES.
	* modules/fnmatch: Append $(FNMATCH_H) to BUILT_SOURCES.
	* modules/utime: Add m4/utimes-null.m4.

