	avoid AC_CONFIG_LINKS.
	* modules/fnmatch (Makefile.am): Use explicit creation rule for
	fnmatch.h, to avoid AC_CONFIG_LINKS.
	* modules/alloca (Makefile.am): Make creation of alloca.h Ctrl-C safe.

