	(AM_FUNC_GETLINE): Invoke AC_GNU_SOURCE. Use <stdlib.h>, not
	<sys/types.h>, for size_t. Use the function name gnu_getline, not
	simply getline. Infoke gl_PREREQ_GETLINE.

