	* m4/jm-macros.m4: Require fetish_FUNC_RMDIR_NOTEMPTY.

	* m4/nanosleep.m4 (jm_FUNC_NANOSLEEP): Save and restore LIBS around
	AC_SEARCH_LIBS call for nanosleep.
	(LIB_NANOSLEEP): Set and AC_SUBST.

