2000-02-08  Akim Demaille  <akim@epita.fr>

	* m4/largefile.m4 (AC_SYS_LARGEFILE_FLAGS): Quote square brackets with
	`[' and `]' and remove uses of `changequote'.
	(AC_SYS_LARGEFILE_MACRO_VALUE): Likewise.
	(AC_SYS_LARGEFILE): Likewise.
