	of changequote.
	* m4/regex.m4 (jm_INCLUDED_REGEX): Likewise.
	* m4/readdir.m4 (jm_FUNC_READDIR): Likewise
	* m4/memcmp.m4 (jm_AC_FUNC_MEMCMP): Likewise, and add `int' for main.
