	(AC_CHECK_FUNCS): Merge all checks from fileutils, textutils, sh-utils.
	(AM_FUNC_STRTOD): Added (from textutils', sh-utils' configure.in).
	(AC_SUBST(POW_LIBM)): Likewise.
	(AC_SUBST(DF_PROG)): Moved from fileutils/configure.in.

