	* m4/gettext.m4 (AM_WITH_NLS): Remove unnecessary lines.
	Fix typo: $nls_cv_header_intl was misspelled as $nsl_cv_header_intl.
	(AM_GNU_GETTEXT): Fix problem with brackets and m4 quoting,
	and simplify the shell code.

